  <brief_title>Role of Rapid On-site Evaluation for Mutational Analysis of EBUS-TBNA Specimens</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mutational Analysis of Endobronchial Ultrasound-guided Transbronchial Needle Aspiration (EBUS-TBNA) Specimens in Patients With Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer: a Randomized Trial of Rapid On-site Evaluation</official_title>
