  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine if rapid on-site evaluation of EBUS-TBNA samples can
      increase the percentage of patients with advanced non-squamous non-small cell lung cancer in
      whom both pathologic subtyping and mutational analysis are obtained.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
